# webeach-design — Project Overview

> **Maintenance rule:** This file is the single source of truth for AI assistants.
> Every time a meaningful change is made to the project — new token group, palette change, new export, changed convention, script update, etc. — this file **must** be updated to reflect it after the task is done.

## What This Is

An npm package of design tokens for the [WebEach](https://webeach.io) services (`@webeach-io/design`). Provides colors, gradients, sizes, and typography in TypeScript + CSS custom properties, with full dark/light mode support.

---

