## Sizes

| Object | Keys | Example values |
|---|---|---|
| `Size` | `'1x'`…`'32x'` | `4px`…`128px` |
| `BorderSize` | `thin`, `regular`, `medium`, `bold`, `extraBold` | `1px`…`8px` |
| `Rounding` | `'1x'`, `'1.5x'`, `'2x'`, `'4x'` | `4px`…`16px` |
| `Spacing` | `'0.5x'`…`'12x'` | `2px`…`48px` |

All size values must be in **`px` units** only.

