## Typography

```
Typography.H1.medium
Typography.H2.medium
Typography.H3.{ regular | medium }
Typography.H4.{ regular | medium }
Typography.H5.{ regular | medium | bold }
Typography.Body.extraSmall.{ regular | medium }
Typography.Body.small.{ regular | medium | bold }
Typography.Body.medium.{ regular | medium | bold }
Typography.Code.regular
```

Fonts: `"Roboto"` (primary), `"Roboto Mono"` (monospace). Font files are **not** included — consumers import from Google Fonts.

