## Scripts

| Command | Description |
|---|---|
| `pnpm build` | tsup: ESM + types + auto-runs `generate:css` |
| `pnpm build:watch` | tsup in watch mode |
| `pnpm generate:css` | Regenerate `dist/tokens.css` standalone |
| `pnpm generate:assets` | Regenerate 126 SVG previews in `assets/` |
| `pnpm test` | Vitest snapshot + Zod validation tests |
| `pnpm test:update` | `vitest run -u` — regenerate snapshots |
| `pnpm lint` / `pnpm lint:fix` | oxlint / oxlint --fix |
| `pnpm fmt` / `pnpm fmt:check` | oxfmt / oxfmt --check |
| `pnpm typecheck` | `tsc --noEmit` |

> **Important:** After any color or gradient change, run `pnpm generate:assets` and commit the new SVGs. Snapshot tests must also be updated with `pnpm test:update`.

---

## Testing

- **Zod schemas** validate key format (`colorKeySchema`: `/^[a-z]+(100|[2-9]00)$/`) and values (`colorValueSchema`: HSL regex)
- **Snapshot tests** for all 4 token modules — protect against accidental value changes
- `DarkModeColor` and `LightModeColor` must have identical keys (enforced by test)
- `DarkModeGradient` and `LightModeGradient` must have identical keys (enforced by test)

---

## Coding Conventions

- **Key names**: `camelCase` — `primary600`, `secondary900`, `extraRelaxed`
- **Exports**: all public tokens and types exported from `src/index.ts`
- **TypeScript**: `satisfies` operator used for token objects (e.g., `satisfies Record<string, HSLValue>`)
- **Types**: each token object exports `Type`, `Key`, and `Value` types (e.g., `SizeType`, `SizeKey`, `SizeValue`)
- **Commit convention**: Conventional Commits enforced by commitlint + Husky `commit-msg` hook

---

## Release

- **`semantic-release`** on push to `main` — auto-versions and publishes to npm
- Branches: `main` (stable) + `next` (prerelease `rc`)
- CI pipeline: `commitlint` → `lint` (oxlint + oxfmt:check + typecheck) → `test` → `build` → `release`
- Publish secret env var: `NPM_TOKEN` (was `YARN_NPM_AUTH_TOKEN`)
- CHANGELOG auto-updated; README tables must be manually updated before releasing color/gradient changes
